erson at the time of saher (before the time of azaan’e fajr) recites YAA BAASE-TO 10 times than he will not be dependent on others, will be relieved from sadness, his sustenance will increase and will get the blessings from where he has not even imagined.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh agar koi shakhs Subh saher ke waqt YAA BAASE-TO ka vird 10 martaba kare to hargiz kisi ka mohtaaj na hoga, ghamo se najaat paayega, us ki rozi khushaadah hogi (badh jaayegi) aur aisi jagah se usey ne’mate’n haasil hongi keh jahan ka usey gumaan bhi na hoga.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ اگر کوئی شخص صبح وقت سحر ’’یَابَاسِطُ‘‘  کا ۱۰ مرتبہ ورد کرے تو ہرگز کسی کا محتاج نہ ہوگا، غموں سے نجات پائے گا، اس کی روزی کشادہ ہوگی اور ایسی جگہ سے اسے نعمتیں حاصل ہوں گی کہ جہاں کا اسے گمان بھی نہ ہوگا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": n